Description:
Chrome extension that adds context menu option to play youtube videos with mpv.

Requirements:
Chrome like browser.
python
mpv (https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv)

Server configuration:
In `youtube-mpv.server.py` modify `PORT` and `[PLAYER, '-really-quiet', '-cache', CACHE, '-af', 'channels=4:4:0:2:0:0:1:3:1:1', yt_url]` to your needs.

Client configuration:
In `youtube-mpv.client.js` modify `trigger_url` to your needs.

Server side:
python youtube-mpv.server.py

Client side:
chrome://extensions/
Load unpacked extensions...
Choose root directory of this project.
